title: Print, "Driving Home the Corn, Harper's Weekly, November 13, 1858, p. 729.", November 13, 1858
creditline: Gift of John Goldsmith Phillips, Jr.
description: Vertical view showing a man and two women coming home with the corn as another man drives the ox-teams on the upper half of the page.
